partyQueue.name: Wake Me Up - Live at the Bedford

lyrics.synced:
[00:13.52] I built a house for love to grow
[00:25.88] I was so young that it was hard to know
[00:36.74] I'm as lost now as I was back then
[00:44.76] Always make a mess of everything
[00:52.43] It's about time that I face myself
[01:02.11] All I do is bleed into someone else
[01:12.57] Painting walls with all my secret tears
[01:19.62] Filling rooms with all my hopes and fears
[01:25.89] But oh my, oh my
[01:35.84] I'll never learn if I never leap
[01:41.76] I'll always yearn if I never speak
[01:50.70] To be loved and love at the highest count
[02:00.75] Means to lose all the things I can't live without
[02:10.57] Let it be known that I will choose to lose
[02:19.83] It's a sacrifice but I can't live a lie
[02:28.11] Let it be known, let it be known that I tried
[02:45.06] I'm so afraid but I'm open wide
[02:54.57] I'll be the one to catch myself this time
[03:04.18] Trying to learn to lean in to it all
[03:10.36] Ain't it funny how the mighty fall?
[03:16.30] Looking back I don't regret a thing
[03:24.15] Yeah, I took some bad turns that I am owning
[03:33.86] I'll stand still and let the storm pass by
[03:40.35] Keep my heart safe 'til the time feels right
[03:45.85] But oh my, oh my
[03:55.23] I'll never learn if I never leap
[04:01.45] I'll always yearn if I never speak
[04:09.40] To be loved and love at the highest count
[04:19.21] Means to lose all the things I can't live without
[04:28.89] Let it be known that I will choose to lose
[04:37.76] It's a sacrifice but I can't live a lie
[04:46.03] Let it be known
[04:49.38] Let it be known that I cried for you
[04:56.44] Even started lying to you
[05:02.13] What a thing to do
[05:07.48] All because I wanted
[05:13.75] To be loved and love at the highest count
[05:23.51] Means to lose all the things I can't live without
[05:32.39] Let it be known, known, known
[05:35.42] That I will choose, I will lose
[05:41.94] It's a sacrifice but I can't live a lie
[05:49.39] Let it be known
[05:52.77] Let it be known that I tried, that I tried
[06:13.01] Let it be known that I tried
